 The accident took place at around 05:25 between a Toyota Hilux and an Isuzu. A passenger in the Isuzu was killed in the collision and the drivers of both vehicles were rushed to Life Midmed Hospital for medical treatment.  The road remains closed as emergency response personnel are trying to recover the deceased from the wreckage. Motorists are urged to make use of alternative routes until the road is open.      The ferals need help #TrafficAlert: R555 closed, seven die in horrific crash Middelburg police officer arrested during Hawks operation  • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za